SUMMARY:Board Game Night At Hillsboro Downtown Station 
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nCome down for board game night! This will be a recurring event\, monthly during the summer and increasing to twice a month in the fall. Zayla and Angie Lloyd will host. Bring a simple game for others to play or play one that we have onsite. Hillsboro Downtown Station has Great food options from around the world\, and lots of great drinks on draft from your favorite local breweries. Come in early and enjoy happy hour from 2-5:30 and save $2 off any draft!
