SUMMARY:Board Game Night at Chronos!
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nA recurring board game night at Chronos Games & Gifts' new larger location! Feel free to look though our game demo library or bring your personal favorites. The event is free with available seating up to about 84 people\, with outside food & drink allowed. Be sure to be kind\, respectful.\nThis is a recurring event that happens every third Friday of the month\, along with a queer board game night every first Friday of the month!\n*If you have any questions feel free to call us at 971-238-6260 or join our [discord here!](https://discord.gg/yYWkfA4DMq)*
